title: German Covid record as WHO warns of Europe deaths
content: Almost 34,000 cases are reported in Germany as the WHO warns of half a million more deaths in Europe.

title: Trump-Russia dossier analyst charged with lying
content: Igor Danchenko, who worked on a largely unsubstantiated 2016 dossier on Donald Trump, is arrested.

title: Indonesia criticises deal to end deforestation
content: The country's environment minister says the country "can't promise what we can't do".

title: LA 'jetpack man' was probably a balloon
content: Investigators think a figure seen flying over Los Angeles was actually a life-size inflatable.

title: High-risk Covid gene more common in South Asians
content: About 60% of people from South Asian backgrounds carry a gene that puts them at higher risk.

title: Nearly all-white jury in black jogger murder trial
content: The judge noted the appearance of discriminatory selection in the trial over Ahmaud Arbery's death.

title: Facebook's metaverse plans labelled 'dystopian'
content: Roger McNamee, an early Facebook investor, says it "should not be allowed" to build the metaverse.
